# GoalifyNow E2E Testing with Playwright

## Overview
GoalifyNow uses Playwright for end-to-end testing. Tests are organized using the Page Object Model pattern and use the test fixtures system for authentication and data management.

---

## Directory Structure

```
tests/
├── config/
│   └── test-config.ts       # Centralized configuration
├── fixtures/
│   └── billing-fixtures.ts  # Mock data fixtures
├── pages/
│   ├── base-page.ts         # Base page class with common methods
