## Running Tests

### Local Development
```bash
# Run all tests
npx playwright test

# Run specific file
npx playwright test tests/specs/finances/finances-smoke.spec.ts

# Run by tag
npx playwright test --grep "@smoke"

# Run single browser
npx playwright test --project=chromium

# Debug mode
npx playwright test --debug

# UI mode
npx playwright test --ui
```

### CI/CD
```bash
# Smoke tests only (fast)
npx playwright test --grep "@smoke @prod"

# Full regression
npx playwright test --grep "@regression"

# Skip local-only tests
npx playwright test --grep-invert "@local"
```

