## Configuration

### Environment Variables
```env
# .env or tests/.env
BASE_URL=http://localhost:4200
TEST_LANDLORD_EMAIL=landlord1@demo.com
TEST_LANDLORD_PASSWORD=Test123!
TEST_TENANT_EMAIL=tenant1@demo.com
TEST_TENANT_PASSWORD=Test123!
E2E_TENANT_ID=default
E2E_DISABLE_AUTO_LOGIN=false
E2E_ALLOW_LEGACY_DEMO_USERS=false
```

Legacy demo aliases (`landlord1@demo.com`, `tenant1@demo.com`, `admin@rentifynow.com`) cause config to throw unless `E2E_ALLOW_LEGACY_DEMO_USERS=true`.

